---
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
import Avatar from '../assets/avatar.webp';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
        title="About Patrick Scheid - Senior Software Engineer"
        description="Senior Software Engineer at DeepL with 9+ years in backend engineering and 2+ years in engineering management. Background spanning AI products, data engineering, and product ownership."
        pageClass="page-about"
>
    <article class="prose">
        <div class="about-header">
            <Image src={Avatar} alt="Patrick Scheid" class="avatar" width={200} height={200}/>
            <h1>About Me</h1>
        </div>

        <p>
            Hi, I'm Patrick Scheid, a Senior Software Engineer at DeepL. With 9+ years building and scaling
            backend systems and 2+ years leading engineering teams, I bridge deep hands-on engineering in C#, Kotlin,
            and Go with a strong understanding of team dynamics, system design trade-offs, and cross-functional alignment.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        <p>
            At DeepL, I contribute to AI-powered writing and translation products with a focus on backend architecture,
            system reliability, and cross-team technical leadership. Previously, as Engineering Manager, I led teams
            of up to 8 engineers integrating LLM research into editing tools serving 500k+ daily users, and scaled
            document translation to 150k+ documents per day.
        </p>

        <h2>Career</h2>

        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Senior Software Engineer <span class="timeline-company">@ DeepL</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Jan 2026 &ndash; Present</span>
                    <p>Returned to an IC role to deepen technical impact. Contributing to AI-powered writing and translation products with a focus on backend architecture, system reliability, and cross-team technical leadership.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Engineering Manager <span class="timeline-company">@ DeepL</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Dec 2023 &ndash; Jan 2026</span>
                    <p>Editor Team: Led 8 engineers bridging AI research and production editing tools serving 500k+ daily users. Drove integration of LLM-based prototypes into product. Document Translation Team: Led 6 engineers scaling document translation to 150k+ docs/day, defined custom quality metrics, and led a focused initiative on PDF layout preservation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Senior Software Engineer <span class="timeline-company">@ DeepL</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Aug &ndash; Dec 2023</span>
                    <p>Designed scalable C# backend services for document translation. Improved processing reliability for complex formats (PPTX, DOCX, PDF) and contributed to architectural decisions that reduced end-to-end translation latency.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Product Owner & Scala Developer <span class="timeline-company">@ Ryte</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Feb 2022 &ndash; Jun 2023</span>
                    <p>Evolved the platform API into an API-as-a-Product: developer experience vision, DX conversion funnel, and monetisation strategy. Led development of authentication, CRM integration, and transactional email services in Scala.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Backend Developer & Scrum Master <span class="timeline-company">@ Exaring (waipu.tv)</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Jul 2019 &ndash; Jan 2022</span>
                    <p>Developed and operated ~60 microservices powering waipu.tv's IPTV platform in Kotlin and Spring Boot. Managed infrastructure on Kubernetes/AWS with Terraform. Part-time Scrum Master for the Business Systems team.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Lead Software Engineer <span class="timeline-company">@ FreshDetect</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Nov 2018 &ndash; Jun 2019</span>
                    <p>Led technical direction for a food-safety startup: evaluated ML approaches for spectroscopy-based freshness detection, prototyped solutions, and provided in-house consulting on architecture and processes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Data & Software Engineer <span class="timeline-company">@ FreshDetect</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">Mar 2016 &ndash; Nov 2018</span>
                    <p>Built internal data analysis tools, data access libraries, and automated validation pipelines. Introduced software development processes. Administered Linux servers and PostgreSQL databases.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>M.Sc. Applied Computer Science <span class="timeline-company">@ Hochschule Trier</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">2015 &ndash; 2018</span>
                    <p>Environmental and Business Informatics.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>B.Sc. Applied Computer Science <span class="timeline-company">@ Hochschule Trier</span></h3>
                    <span class="timeline-date">2011 &ndash; 2016</span>
                    <p>Engineering focus. Including roles as research assistant, software developer, and tutor.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>How I Work</h2>
        <p>
            I believe the best solutions emerge when teams understand the "why" behind what they build. I combine
            technical depth with a strong emphasis on collaboration, clear communication, and pragmatic
            problem-solving. I care about getting the right things done well — not just shipping fast.
        </p>

        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>
            I'm always open to conversations about technology, product development, and team leadership —
            whether that's exchanging ideas, exploring collaborations, or discussing new opportunities.
            Feel free to reach out!
        </p>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 2em 0;
    }

    .avatar {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 1em;
        display: block;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    }

    .prose {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 1em;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .timeline {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 2.5rem;
        margin: 1.5em 0 2em;
    }

    .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0.55rem;
        top: 0.25rem;
        bottom: 0.25rem;
        width: 2px;
        background: var(--color-border);
    }

    .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

    .timeline-item:last-child {
        padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .timeline-dot {
        position: absolute;
        left: -2.25rem;
        top: 0.35rem;
        width: 14px;
        height: 14px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--color-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--color-bg);
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .timeline-content h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.15em;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .timeline-company {
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }

    .timeline-date {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 0.35em;
    }

    .timeline-content p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>
